OL,3,CHow to get help and support for drug
OL,4,Caddiction in London
OL,6,FDrug deaths in the capital are the
OL,7,Fhighest they have been in 25 years,
OL,8,Faccording to new statistics from the
OL,9,FONS.
OL,11,FAcross the country, London had the
OL,12,Flowest rate for drug poisoning and
OL,13,Fdrug misuse, with 58.1 deaths per
OL,14,Fmillion people and 41.0 per million.
OL,15,FBut it is still the highest it's been
OL,16,Fin 25 years.
