OL,3,CHow to get help and support for drug
OL,4,Caddiction in London
OL,6,FA close friend of the Beckhams who
OL,7,Fonce admitted to wasting #1 million on
OL,8,FClass A drugs is now using art to help
OL,9,Fothers who are struggling to turn
OL,10,Ftheir life around.
OL,12,FWith the right help and support, it's
OL,13,Fpossible for you to get drug-free and
OL,14,Fstay that way, and help is available
OL,15,Fon the NHS - although services are
OL,16,Fvery stretched.
OL,18,FHere is how to find help and support
OL,19,Fif you or someone you know is seeking
OL,20,Ftreatment for drug addiction.
