OL,3,CHow to get help and support for drug
OL,4,Caddiction in London
OL,6,FWhere to get help for drugs
OL,8,FThe NHS suggests you speak to your GP,
OL,9,Fwho may refer you to a local drug
OL,10,Fservice.
OL,12,FYou can also go directly to your local
OL,13,Fdrug treatment service yourself.
OL,15,FVisit the Frank website to find
OL,16,Fsupport near you. If you're having
OL,17,Ftrouble finding the right sort of
OL,18,Fhelp, call the Frank drugs helpline on
OL,19,F0300 123 6600 who can talk you through
OL,20,Fall your options.
