OL,6,FCharity and private drugs treatment
OL,8,FThere are charities and private drug
OL,9,Fand alcohol treatment organisations
OL,10,Fthat can help you. Visit the Adfam
OL,11,Fwebsite page, Finding Support, to see
OL,12,Fa list of useful organisations.
OL,14,FPrivate drug treatment can be very
OL,15,Fexpensive, but you may be able to be
OL,16,Freferred through the NHS.
OL,18,FHelp you may be offered:
